Recently Masjid committee have installed Air Conditioner for the ease of the musallis
The best part of the Masjid is that the Management Committee of this masjid allows the community and the surrounding Apartment residents to conduct their community based programs here. Very soon arrangements for spaces for women is being arranged here. Overall it can be a model what an Ideal Masjid should be in its functionality
